text: Eunidia lateralis is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Charles Joseph Gahan in 1893.BioLib.cz - Eunidia lateralis. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Eunidiini Category:Beetles described in 1893 Category:Taxa named by Charles Joseph Gahan
